  "detailed_description": "Take part in the adventures of SUPER BOT, an action adventure game from a third person perspective. The main character is a cute robot, which, due to the domination of the industrial planet by nasty bugs, sets out to fight to regain energy and save his friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643600/extras/6c4d23b5876dbfe59ff446bb9990ea3c.poster.avif?t=1682943579\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643600/extras/6c4d23b5876dbfe59ff446bb9990ea3c.webm?t=1682943579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>On the way you will chase worms and fight the guardians to regain energy and save your friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643600/extras/6224264e351a01503bd8b28551c7c644.poster.avif?t=1682943579\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643600/extras/6224264e351a01503bd8b28551c7c644.webm?t=1682943579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643600/extras/6224264e351a01503bd8b28551c7c644.mp4?t=1682943579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br>- Pleasant and addictive gameplay.<br>- Beautiful 3D graphics.<br>- Ability to play via the Xbox controller.<br>- Low minimum hardware requirements.<br>- The game does not have a save system",
